  <section version="5.0" xml:id="introduction">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>In XMLmind XML Editor, the support of DocBook 5 (a RELAX NG schema)
    is built on the top of the support of DocBook 4 (a DTD). That's why
    everything described in <link
    xlink:href="http://www.xmlmind.com/xmleditor/_distrib/doc/docbook/index.html"><citetitle>XMLmind
    XML Editor - DocBook Support</citetitle></link> (also available using
    <guimenu>Help</guimenu>|<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem>) also applies to
    DocBook 5 documents.</para>

    <para>This document quickly describes what is specific to DocBook
    5.</para>
  </section>

